英國歌手'''[[哈利·史泰敖|哈利·史泰敖]]'''以個人名義發行了兩張[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]、一張[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]、一張[[音樂錄影帶|視像專輯]]、九支[[單曲|單曲]]、八個[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]，以及一支[[宣傳單曲|宣傳單曲]]。史泰敖的音樂事業於2010年作為男性組合[[1世代|1世代]]的成員開始<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/24/arts/music/one-direction-and-the-wanted-boy-bands-return.html?_r=2|title=Boy Bands Are Back, Wholesome or Sexy|last=Mckinley Jr.|first=James C.|work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|date=2012-03-23|accessdate=2021-01-18|subscription=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522205414/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/24/arts/music/one-direction-and-the-wanted-boy-bands-return.html?_r=2|archive-date=2013-05-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rs">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/harry-styles-new-direction-119432/|title=Harry Styles’ New Direction|last=Crowe|first=Cameron|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|date=2017-04-18|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810230312/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/harry-styles-new-direction-119432/|archive-date=2020-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著團體於2016年停止音樂活動<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9419436/one-direction-ten-year-anniversary-fan-interviews|title=10 Years of One Direction: The Story of the World’s Biggest Boy Band, Told With the Fans Who Made It Happen|last=Paul|first=Larisha|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2020-07-16|accessdate=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206170314/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9419436/one-direction-ten-year-anniversary-fan-interviews|archive-date=2020-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同年他跟[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]簽署唱片合約成為個人歌手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6859541/harry-styles-management-jeffrey-azoff-modest|title=Harry Styles Splits With One Direction's Management, Joins Azoff|last=Schneider|first=Marc|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2017-02-01|accessdate=2021-01-18|subscription=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114170959/http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6859541/harry-styles-management-jeffrey-azoff-modest|archive-date=2020-11-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Columbia">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7416429/harry-styles-solo-record-deal-one-direction|title=Harry Styles Signs Recording Contract With Columbia: Exclusive|last=Halperin|first=Shirley|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2016-06-23|access-date=2017-10-16|subscription=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019111119/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7416429/harry-styles-solo-record-deal-one-direction|archive-date=2017-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。史泰敖在2017年4月發行個人出道單曲〈[[時代印記|時代印記]]〉<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7744377/harry-styles-solo-single-cover-art-sign-of-the-times|title=Harry Styles Debuts Cover Art for First Solo Single, 'Sign of the Times'|last=Tom|first=Lauren|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2017-03-31|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403070610/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7744377/harry-styles-solo-single-cover-art-sign-of-the-times|archive-date=2017-04-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲登上[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]冠軍，以及美國[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]第4位，亦登上澳洲單曲榜冠軍位置。歌曲亦獲[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]][[音乐唱片销售认证列表|認證]]為四白金唱片，並獲[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|澳大利亚唱片业协会]]認證為四白金唱片。

單曲發行一個月後，史泰敖發行了[[哈利時代|個人同名專輯]]，並收錄〈時代印記〉<ref name="harrystyles">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7760233/harry-styles-self-titled-debut-may-12-tracklist|title=Harry Styles Self-Titled Debut Due May 12, Check Out Tracklist|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2017-04-13|access-date=2017-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623084612/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7760233/harry-styles-self-titled-debut-may-12-tracklist|archive-date=2017-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯登上澳洲、加拿大、愛爾蘭、英國以及美國專輯榜冠軍位置，並獲美國當地唱片業協會認證為白金唱片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/how-harry-styles-debut-album-has-performed-in-the-charts-across-the-world__19250/|title=How Harry Styles' debut album has performed in the charts across the world|last=White|first=Jack|publisher=[[官方榜单公司|Official Charts Company]]|date=2017-05-24|access-date=2017-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171017043437/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/how-harry-styles-debut-album-has-performed-in-the-charts-across-the-world__19250/|archive-date=2017-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯於全球售出超過100萬張，成為2017年其中一張最暢銷的專輯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2018.pdf|title=Global Music Report 2018|publisher=[[國際唱片業協會|International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]]|access-date=2020-05-26|page=9|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328194010/http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2018.pdf|archive-date=2018-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯亦發行了〈[[兩個鬼魂|兩個鬼魂]]〉與〈[[奇異果_(歌曲)|奇異果]]〉兩支後續單曲。

史泰敖在2019年發行了他的第二張錄音室專輯《[[搖滾界線|搖滾界線]]》，並在專輯發行前釋出〈[[聚光之下|聚光之下]]〉與〈[[迷戀妳|迷戀妳]]〉兩支單曲，兩支單曲均打進多國單曲榜前10位，當中包括澳洲與英國。《搖滾界線》於同年稍後時間發行，在發行首週空降美國[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《告示牌》二百強專輯榜]]冠軍位置，刷新英國男歌手在美國的專輯最高首週銷量紀錄。史泰敖亦成為首位前兩張專輯均空降《告示牌》二百強專輯榜冠軍的英國男歌手<ref name="Billboard 200">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8546971/harry-styles-fine-line-album-no-1-billboard-200-chart|title=Harry Styles' 'Fine Line' Album Earns Huge No. 1 Debut on Billboard 200 Chart|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2019-12-22|access-date=2019-12-23|subscription=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200119022457/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8546971/harry-styles-fine-line-album-no-1-billboard-200-chart|archive-date=2020-01-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯其後獲[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]認證為白金唱片，並獲美國唱片業協會認證為雙白金唱片。專輯其後亦發行了〈[[迷失自我|迷失自我]]〉、〈[[甜蜜滋味|甜蜜滋味]]〉、〈[[金黃耀眼|金黃耀眼]]〉與〈[[以善待人|以善待人]]〉四支單曲。專輯的第四支單曲〈甜蜜滋味〉成功登上美國《告示牌》百強單曲榜冠軍位置，成為史泰敖在當地的首支冠軍單曲，更獲得多地的多白金唱片認證，包括在加拿大認證為五白金唱片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9431815/harry-styles-watermelon-sugar-hot-100|title=Harry Styles' 'Watermelon Sugar' Surges to Top of Billboard Hot 100, Becoming His First No. 1|last=Trust|first=Gary|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2020-08-10|access-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815155715/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9431815/harry-styles-watermelon-sugar-hot-100|archive-date=2020-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

